name: Non-Default What Do You Like To Eat Intent

speech: Some foods, I like a lot. I like to eat desserts in the blender. My wife also makes great vegetable soups with it, and I really like mashed potatoes and fruits blended up. But, I gotta say, sometimes my wife blends a burger for me, and that's hard for me to take. It's just not the same. I really just want to eat what everyone else is eating.
